title: Westcott 15106 TrimAir 12-Inch Guillotine Paper Cutter, Heavy-Duty Multi-Paper Trimmer with 30 Sheet Capacity
description: The Westcott Trim Air wood paper guillotine offers unmatched style, design, and performance. Enhanced with proprietary titanium-bonded blade technology that keeps the blade sharper longer, our straight-edge cutter easily slices through 30 sheets of 20lb paper at a time. A comfortable ergonomic handle comes coated with anti-microbial protection engineered to inhibit the growth of bacterial odors. A natural wooden base makes for an attractive, contemporary design that will complement your home, office, or classroom decor.
